{"tid":1384053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左買物資，捐八達通得唔得？","createTime":"2019-07-29T23:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T23:54:01.000Z","uid":3295,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54886c4b91d2b67f8f36416b57ef36dd9e1842e6","tid":1384053,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:25:41.000Z","msg":"捐物資呢啲就一定要啦，但除左物資，衫褲鞋襪袋其實都要掉，個個星期出既話負擔都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但衫褲鞋襪又個個人唔同size，走個陣又冇可能著返黑tee，咁捐八達通得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\npros:<br />\n- 大多數食肆連鎖店都收，食飯又得，買物資又得，玩變裝party亦得<br />\n- 冇用voucher俾錢咁覺眼<br />\n- flexible點用都得，唔洗買足額<br />\n- mark低餘額擺返去物資站可增值循環利用<br />\n- 退左張卡可以拎按金<br />\n- 唔洗過數唔驚會俾有心人士呃錢<br />\n- 需要既人自由決定點樣使用<br />\n<br />\ncons:<br />\n- 神智混亂既時候可能唔小心用黎搭車<br />\n- ssp啲鋪頭唔收<br />\n- 唔知買嗰個有冇法律責任，但見到八達通個網直情有form俾人大量購入，我估應該得（望補充）<br />\n<br />\n而家諗到可以擺入面有錢既八達通係物資站、教會、錫克廟呢啲地方，等需要既人自己攞，用完之後mark低餘額擺返去，有錢既人就幫手增值完再擺返去，giving end同receiving end完全唔洗知對方身份，避免曝光危險<br />\n<br />\n覺得可行既話唔該幫手推俾更多人睇到<br />\n記住唔好咁傻豬走出去同人食飯呀！！！！"},{"pid":"bfa3e54755acb39ceed480bccabd42919f507d0a","tid":1384053,"uid":292926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59ed77c61482566d30effe418340984565741c9a","tid":1384053,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"我要財務自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6abf03a1c15d5e73313093d64a44f7fb2f59d16","tid":1384053,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:34:53.000Z","msg":"唔好唔知頭唔知路就出去同人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772cbadb936ddd92ad4f120273a491b639016243","tid":1384053,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:35:23.000Z","msg":"[窮學生] 我只需要你地管理好物！資！仲有上！前！線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ab33834b3d1d235df2ef10c8937383267d0b158","tid":1384053,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:36:03.000Z","msg":"其實係無現金券咁覺眼 用完返還返比人再充值"},{"pid":"7b7969d5ea471002bb33836b8a859b59a097086f","tid":1384053,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ab33834b3d1d235df2ef10c8937383267d0b158","tid":1384053,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:36:03.000Z","msg":"其實係無現金券咁覺眼 用完返還返比人再充值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:37:28.000Z","msg":"payment method通常會記低，我都驚買餐券既話睇番cctv就知係咩人，八達通使用率高啲（好似係）"},{"pid":"ffb4dc5b8099df83fb04983cc93411d72d374d19","tid":1384053,"uid":3295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:42:11.000Z","msg":"copied from 格離post <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">八達通攞左唔好直接用，帶口罩cap帽直接攞去退錢，因為你唔知會唔會有狗混左入家長群，擺啲mark 左no既卡嚟trace你地，如果喺七仔呢啲有cctv既地方嘟嚟用又無戴罩，佢就知你咩樣，所以小心啲</code></pre>"},{"pid":"19bc8d9fb6082d699e86618a5082f54a8aff5194","tid":1384053,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:44:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c20d66f4da7d0d87e80fb0e05a49be4708dd5f8","tid":1384053,"uid":219444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:54:01.000Z","msg":"有心、不過Coupon會安全啲"}]}